These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, reading
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, accountant
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, biathlon
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, bus
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the firefighter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | reading       | board-games |
| Job         | accountant | firefighter  |
| Sport       | biathlon    | lacrosse    |
| Transport   | bus       | train      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, electrician
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, adventure
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, tennis
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the freelancer is on the far left##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | fanta     | 7up |
| Job           | freelancer | electrician      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | horror      |
| Sport         | water-polo | tennis     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, tea
There 2 different types of food: pear, strawberry
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, r&b
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, tram
1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking water is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person eating pear is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | water | tea  |
| Food          | pear    | strawberry   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b  | metal   |
| Transport     | tram     | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, spinach
The people have 2 different jobs:  software-developer, freelancer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, house
1. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
2. the software-developer is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking fanta is the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | sprite       | fanta |
| Food          | spinach         | pineapple    |
| Job           | freelancer | software-developer    |
| Music-Genre   | soul           | house   |

