.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-10::.
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, carrot
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, gospel
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, thai
2 different pets are kept: dog, hamster
1. the thai is the owner of the hamster##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
3. the thai is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Food          | pineapple | carrot |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | gospel      |
| Nationality   | italian | thai    |
| Pet           | dog    | hamster    |

