The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, adventure
2 different pets are kept: pony, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, airplane
1. the software-developer is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
2. the software-developer is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
3. the owner of the pony is the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | analyst | software-developer     |
| Movie-Genre   | family          | adventure |
| Pet           | pony          | rat    |
| Transport     | airplane            | motorbike       |

 